Aurora::Component::Pipeline::Serializer::XHTML2PDF
==================================================

DESCRIPTION

This pipeline component takes the current response content
representing an XHTML document and serializes it to PDF.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires:

   Aurora  (>= 0.4.0)
   HTMLDOC (>= 1.8.14) 

HTMLDOC is available from http://www.easysw.com.

CAVEATS

* HTMLDOC currently doesn't support UTF-8
* External files required to generate the PDF must reside on the local
  filesystem

